Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When Zeus told them of their past, the human race remembered how to place seeds and till fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl, your pronunciation is wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm trying very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've gotten so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first came here, I thought\Nyou were a horrible student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that he's traveling the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see him again some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:32.09,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}The Real Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You started working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an interior coordinator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I would suspect that you have a keen eye for home decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I said interior but it's a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a kitchen coordinator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like me, who's never set foot\Nin a kitchen before, has this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I might ask you to help me with my kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But a kitchen you design would probably be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been drinking, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not even a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great. Take it one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you must rush, there is always tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what happiness is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tired of hearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was happy just knowing\NI was waiting at the station for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,People are so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadness fades away and only happy memories remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People were built pretty conveniently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how we can continue living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you. This is Mr. Verdemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the one who cleared all the charges against you, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out all I could about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were at 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You traveled around the world as an East German\Nintelligence agent who pretended to be a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, you continued your investigation on human rights violations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as a freelance journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a lot of material on that subject in your large bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:05:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing I could never find out was your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolfgang Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He left without telling us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an inspector anymore, Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you became a professor at the police academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been able to have conversations with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not real conversations, I guess. E-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we're parent and child,\Nwe've never really talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lived our lives without knowing one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How much can people convey to others in just one lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have so much we want to say\Nwhile drinking a cold beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going back to Dusseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The company I work for is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things there that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"You can't ran away."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"You have to face reality and keep moving forward."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you dispose of this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen and I are willing to help you at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So is Dieter and him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Send all of them my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma's hearing continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge's testimony begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the worst serial murder case in all of European history?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma proven completely innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Law authorities express their apologies to Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The motive behind the incidents is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he true identity of the mysterious\Nyoung man behind the whole incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Medical College of Munster University\Noffers Dr. Tenma a position as a professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma positively declines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma joins the MSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The articles gradually get smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,People are built conveniently, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, you've gotten bigger while I haven't been looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten slimier when I wasn't looking, Mr. Heckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have a big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm going to soccer practice,\Nso don't follow me any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Tenma back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing that "Doctors Without Borders" crap to look cool, but it won't make him any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get a hold of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After I think about the expenses and the work\NI put into the job he asked me to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the payment doesn't seem like it was nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma asked you to do a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said I just had to find someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to steal some secret police documents.\NWhat happens if they catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give Tenma this request form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him that if he won't pay, I'll have him work as a black market doctor again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:20.95,Names2,,0,0,40,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}Southern France
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. We haven't seen you here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a foreign nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy these with everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The leaves are photosynthesing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of Mendel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he discovered the Law of Inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the same college as he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brno University.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In a large city, south east of the Czech Republic, in the Moravian region.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have a good time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel great today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even scary stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something you want to ask me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the twins' mother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And that man killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that man's experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die, the children growing inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,will definitely punish that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the real monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids are alive, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Remembered what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I might never remember again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave them names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Their names are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You really live up to your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late by ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Professor Kronecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. You know why I've called you here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It concerns your graduation thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a lot has happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be hard coming back to school after taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that's no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, your thesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best paper I've ever seen from any one of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think very highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that you will save many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The court will not allow you to be late,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you graduate? I'll be with you even if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to console me the next time we see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell by your voice that you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Although it's going to\Nbe even tougher from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate. Come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't come straight home. I have work\Nand I made plans with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he's got to leave again right away with the MSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to be home tomorrow.\NSo you have to come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina. About tomorrow's plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma... I'm going to see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:56.59,Monster-Title,,0,0,40,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}Bayern State-Run Police Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,80,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,80,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been asleep all this time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want you to hear, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That time... when that monster appeared in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one will I leave and which one will I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:20:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which one will I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my mother trying to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did she get my sister and I mixed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of us was the unwanted one?
